channel.description:
SUBSCRIBE FOR A COOKIE!

Hello, welcome to my Bazylland channel
Enjoy watching my Farming Simulator 22 videos daily and subscribe to my channel!

How I Make Videos:

I play Farming Simulator 19/22 along with the game mods and create different scenes and maps for each movie.

I make thumbnails by taking a screenshot of my Farming Simulator 19/22 game.
Later, I edit these screenshots and create the thumbnails.

All footage used in my video is 100% captured and I am my property.

* Every gameplay clip on this channel is recorded and edited by me (NO RE-USE OF CONTENT).

#LS22 #bazylland  #tractor @bazylland-tractors & Excavators

videos.description:
POS≈ÅUCHAJ W SERWISACH STREAMINGOWYCH: https://mugo.lnk.to/Futbol2024 

POLSKA DO BOJU!

Muzyka: Bartosz 'Tabb' Zielony
S≈Çowa: Jacek 'Mezo' Mejer, Marcin 'Du≈ºe Pe' Matuszewski

***

Pi≈Çka jest jedna a bramki sƒÖ dwie...

Pierwszy "Futbol" nagrali≈õmy w 2003 roku - czyli 21 lat temu. Zrobili≈õmy to z czystej zajawki - bo stojƒÖc u progu 'kariery rapera' obaj byli≈õmy r√≥wnoczesnie fanatykami wƒôdka... wr√≥ƒá, futbolu ;) Do tego jeden z nas (Mezo) chwilƒô wcze≈õniej sko≈Ñczy≈Ç kompletnƒÖ juniorskƒÖ karierƒô w Lechu Pozna≈Ñ, drugi za≈õ (Du≈ºe Pe) w wieku 21 lat w≈Ça≈õnie doprowadzi≈Ç do swojego pierwszego transferu zawodnika do klubu najwy≈ºszej klasy rozgrywkowej w Polsce.

A "Futbol"? Mimo braku klipu i nieobecno≈õci na jakimkolwiek albumie sta≈Ç siƒô swego rodzaju hitem, przewijajƒÖcym siƒô w muzyczno-pi≈Çkarskim konek≈õcie jeszcze przez d≈Çugie lata.

Teraz przewi≈Ñmy szybko ta≈õmƒô w prz√≥d do 2024 roku. Ostatni z pi≈Çkarskich bohater√≥w oryginalnego "Futbolu" sko≈Ñczyl w≈Ça≈õnie boiskowƒÖ  karierƒô. Jeden z nas (Du≈ºe Pe) czƒô≈õciej dzia≈Ça dzi≈õ jako agent pi≈Çkarski ni≈º jako raper - i ma na koncie m. in. poprowadzenie polskich odcink√≥w kariery Igora Angulo i Daniego Ramireza. Drugi (Mezo) wspiƒÖ≈Ç siƒô w kraju na szczyty muzycznej popularno≈õci, p≈ÇacƒÖc za to jednak s≈ÇonƒÖ cenƒô w postaci hejtu rapowego ≈õwiatka.

≈ªadnemu z nas nie minƒô≈Ça jednak przez te wszystkie lata ani zajawka na rymowanie, ani zajawka na futbol. Kiedy wiƒôc wsp√≥lny znajomy niespodziewanie rzuci≈Ç w eter pytanie: "Ej, a dlaczego nie nagracie nowej wersji 'Futbolu' z nazwiskami wsp√≥≈Çczesnych pi≈Çkarzy?" - wystarczy≈Ço kilka telefon√≥w, trzy dni zdalnej pracy w Warszawie i w Poznaniu - i ze studia Tabba wyjecha≈Ç "Futbol 2024".

...wciƒÖ≈º dokonujemy zmian w tej grze!

It is a channel for entertainment and fun devoted to animation and games.
Excavators and tractors are game videos and cartoon animations about construction and agricultural machines and vehicles. See how the excavator digs and what sounds it makes. See how a tractor works on a farm and what the farm life is like. You will see more and learn what excavators and tractors as well as trucks and bulldozers look like. You will definitely have a nice time :)
Let's play farm simulator games together, see how tractors and bulldozer or mini excavator work, see agricultural machinery and their use, see how vehicles are built and listen to the music and sound of vehicles and machines  - Video for everyone.

channel.name: Michele Morrone
channel.description: Michele Morrone is a global actor and singer and was the breakout star of Netflix's blockbuster franchise 365 DAYS. Morrone can most recently be seen starring opposite Megan Fox in the Millennium film SUBSERVIENCE that was released in September, 2024. Last winter, he completed shooting the independent film HOME SWEET HOME REBIRTH based on the vastly popular video game. Morrone just wrapped his starring role opposite Blake Lively and Anna Kendrick in SIMPLEFAVOR 2 directed by Paul Feig, the sequel to the successful first installment for Amazon coming out later this year. An accomplished recording artist, Michele has released music internationally through various labels and has performed live concert dates in addition to having over 1.1 monthly listeners on Spotify and over 23 million followers on his social media accounts. Leave Me is his first release with 477 Records. Morrone is also the global face of the celebrated Italian brand Dolce and Gabbana.

videos.title: Bacefook & Discobeat - Went to Poland 2020
videos.description:
Single available in digital services: https://MagicRecords.lnk.to/WTP2020
 
2020 needs some positive music ‚Äì so we made a new & fresh version of ‚ÄûWent to Poland‚Äú in co-operation with DISCOBEAT  
 
The Original version of Bacefook's "Went to Poland" has been released in 2012. A great hype strarted and the song became a real ClubSmasher in Poland and some other countries around.
The Project Bacefook was born and the guys behind had already contact to the Polish DJ DiscoBeat who grew up and lives in Austria.
Both acts followed different music-genres and lost sight of for a few years. But they re-freshed the contact in 2019 and the idea was born that Discobeat creates a Disco Polo version of "Went to Poland" what he realized in early 2020 and the result shows that the song seems to have really waited for this update and conquer Poland and the World again...
